[Article in German]

Walz MK(1), Albrecht KH, Niebel W, Eigler FW.

Author information:
(1)Abteilung f√ºr Allgemeine Chirurgie, Universit√§tsklinikum Essen.

Thirty new malignant tumours were found in 1080 patients (634 men, 446 women; 
mean age 37.6 +/- 13.6 years) after a median follow-up period of 5 years 
following 1245 cadaveric kidney transplantations performed between 1972 and 
1990. The mean dialysis period before transplantation had been 4.0 +/- 3.1 
